What to do to publicise a new BlueJ release.

1. Update the BlueJ web site.

2. Send a message to bluej-announce@bluej.org.

3. Make announcements to the following web sites:

   http://www.apple.com/downloads/macosx/submit/
   http://www.techtracker.com/mp/devapp.m
   http://freshmeat.net/
   http://www.macupdate.com/email/submission.php

   and newsgroups:

   comp.lang.java.softwaretools
